  <entry>
    <title>LeetCode.27.移出元素</title>
    <link href="/2023/11/07/LeetCode-27-%E7%A7%BB%E5%87%BA%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0/"/>
    <url>/2023/11/07/LeetCode-27-%E7%A7%BB%E5%87%BA%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="我的题解"><a href="#我的题解" class="headerlink" title="我的题解"></a>我的题解</h1><p>代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">removeElement</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> val)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 双指针问题</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// i指针指向需要交换的元素</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">j</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// j指针去寻找可以进行交换的元素</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (i &lt; nums.length &amp;&amp; j &lt; nums.length) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[i] == val) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 如果i需要进行交换</span><br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (j &lt; nums.length &amp;&amp; nums[j] == val) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// j去寻找可以交换的元素</span><br>                    j++;<br>                &#125;<br>            &#125;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (j &lt; nums.length) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 如果j找到了,就进行交换</span><br>                <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">t</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums[i];<br>                nums[i] = nums[j];<br>                nums[j] = t;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 否则退出循环,说明整个数组已经遍历完了</span><br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>            &#125;<br>            i++; <span class="hljs-comment">// 两个指针向后移动</span><br>            j++;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> i; <span class="hljs-comment">// 返回有效元素个数,i=有效下标+1,恰好就是有效元素个数</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="我的思考"><a href="#我的思考" class="headerlink" title="我的思考"></a>我的思考</h1><p>看到这道题的第一眼，我只是想到了暴力解法，完全没有想到双指针（快慢指针）求解，并且在看了别的大佬的快慢指针写法后，忍不住惊叹<strong>这TM写的也太简洁了吧，草！</strong>因此，非常有必要去深入了解双指针的多种写法以及这种思考方式</p><ul><li>暴力求解，hhh：</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">removeElement</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> val)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">size</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; size; i++) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 第一个for循环遍历数组中所有元素</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[i] == val) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 发现有需要移出的元素,将后边的所有元素前移</span><br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">j</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> i + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; j &lt; size; j++) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// i + 1的写法防止越界</span><br>                    nums[j - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = nums[j];<br>                &#125;<br>                size--; <span class="hljs-comment">// 数组大小--,有效元素个数减少</span><br>                i--; <span class="hljs-comment">// 因为每次循环后i都++,i--可以让下一次循环还是i,再次检查当前位置是否还是需要移出的元素</span><br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> size; <span class="hljs-comment">// 返回有效元素的个数</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>双指针法主要包括两种：</p><ul><li>快慢指针法：快慢指针都从同一端开始移动，快指针每次都移动一步，慢指针只有当快指针不等于val时，即找到有效值时才移动一步</li><li>左右指针法：左指针在左端，右指针在右端；左指针向右移动，寻找等于val的元素，即需要交换的元素；右指针向左移动，寻找不等于val的元素</li><li>（当然这两种移动策略只适用于这道题，不同情况下还需要制定不同的移动策略哦！）</li></ul></li><li><p>快慢指针法：</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">removeElement</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> val)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">slow</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// 定义快慢指针</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">fast</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (fast++ &lt; nums.length) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 快指针每次都在++</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[fast] != val) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 如果快指针找到了有效元素,就覆盖到慢指针,同时慢指针++</span><br>                nums[slow++] = nums[fast];<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> slow; <span class="hljs-comment">// 返回有效元素个数</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>左右指针法：</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">removeElement</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> val)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">left</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// 定义左右指针</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">right</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (left &lt;= right) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (left &lt;= right &amp;&amp; nums[left] != val) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 左指针向右寻找需要移出的元素</span><br>                left++;<br>            &#125;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (left &lt;= right &amp;&amp; nums[right] == val) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 右指针向左找有效元素</span><br>                right--;<br>            &#125;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (left &lt;= right) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 如果找到了,将右指针找到的有效元素覆盖到左指针需要移出的元素</span><br>                nums[left++] = nums[right--];<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> left; <span class="hljs-comment">// 返回有效元素个数,即有效元素下标+1</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
