  <entry>
    <title>LeetCode.704.二分查找</title>
    <link href="/2023/11/06/LeetCode-704-%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE/"/>
    <url>/2023/11/06/LeetCode-704-%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="我的题解"><a href="#我的题解" class="headerlink" title="我的题解"></a>我的题解</h1><p>代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">search</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> target)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">left</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">right</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (left &lt; right) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">mid</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> left + (right - left) / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// 防止溢出</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[mid] &gt;= target) &#123;<br>                right = mid;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123; <br>                left = mid + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> nums[left] == target ? left : -<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="我的思考"><a href="#我的思考" class="headerlink" title="我的思考"></a>我的思考</h1><p>网上对于二分查找有很多种写法，他们的边界条件、行为逻辑等都有一定的不同之处，比如：</p><ul><li>边界条件：<code>while (left &lt; right)</code>、<code>while (left &lt;= right)</code></li><li>right的行为逻辑：<code>right = mid</code>、<code>right = mid - 1</code></li><li>left的行为逻辑：<code>left = mid + 1</code>、<code>left = mid</code></li><li>是否需要后续处理：<code>return nums[left] == target ? left : -1</code></li></ul><p>因此，在查阅大量资料后，我发现二分查找大致存在<strong>三种写法</strong></p><h2 id="第一种写法"><a href="#第一种写法" class="headerlink" title="第一种写法"></a>第一种写法</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">search</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> target)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">left</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">right</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (left &lt;= right) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 将查找区间设置在[left, right],即[0, nums.length - 1]</span><br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">mid</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> left + (right - left) / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>; <br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[mid] == target) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 找到就直接返回</span><br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> mid;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[mid] &gt; target) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 此时target可能在[left, mid - 1]</span><br>                right = mid - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 此时target可能在[mid + 1, right]</span><br>                left = mid + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 循环退出后left==right+1，所有元素都比较过了</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> -<span class="hljs-number">1</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// 没有找到</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="第二种写法（版本1）"><a href="#第二种写法（版本1）" class="headerlink" title="第二种写法（版本1）"></a>第二种写法（版本1）</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">search</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> target)</span> &#123;<br> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">left</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">right</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (left &lt; right) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 将查找区间设置在[left, right),即[0, nums.length - 1)</span><br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">mid</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> left + (right - left) / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[mid] == target) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 找到就直接返回</span><br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> mid;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[mid] &gt; target) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 此时target可能在[left, mid)</span><br>                right = mid;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 此时target可能在[mid + 1, right)</span><br>                left = mid + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 循环退出后left == right,始终保留一个值还没有进行比较</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> nums[left] == target ? left : -<span class="hljs-number">1</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// 比较最后一个元素是否是目标值</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="第二种写法（版本2）"><a href="#第二种写法（版本2）" class="headerlink" title="第二种写法（版本2）"></a>第二种写法（版本2）</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">search</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> target)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">left</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">right</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (left &lt; right) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 将查找区间设置在[left, right),即[0, nums.length)</span><br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">mid</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> left + (right - left) / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[mid] == target) &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> mid;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[mid] &gt; target) &#123;<br>                right = mid;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>                left = mid + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 循环退出后left==right,虽然任然收缩为一个元素，但所有有效元素都已经比较过了</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> -<span class="hljs-number">1</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// 没有找到</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="第二种写法（版本3）"><a href="#第二种写法（版本3）" class="headerlink" title="第二种写法（版本3）"></a>第二种写法（版本3）</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">search</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> target)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">left</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">right</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (left &lt; right) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">mid</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> left + (right - left) / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">// 比较运算符必须为 &gt;= ,如果为 &gt; ,那么else中的 &lt;= 就会将可能是target的下标跳过，即mid + 1</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[mid] &gt;= right) &#123; <br>                right = mid;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>                left = mid + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 不在循环过程中进行比较，当循环结束后收缩为一个值时，再比较是否找到目标值</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> nums[left] == target ? left : -<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="第三种写法"><a href="#第三种写法" class="headerlink" title="第三种写法"></a>第三种写法</h2><pre><code class="java">class Solution &#123;    public int search(int[] nums, int target) &#123;        int left = 0;        int right = nums.length - 1;        while (left + 1 &lt; right) &#123; // 将查找区间设置在(left, right),即(0, nums.length - 1)            int mid = left + (right - left) / 2;            if (nums[mid] == target) &#123; // 找到直接返回                return mid;            &#125; else if (nums[mid] &gt; target) &#123; // 此时target可能在(left, mid)                right = mid;            &#125; else &#123; // 此时target可能在(mid, right)                left = mid;            &#125;        &#125;        // 退出循环后，始终保留两个未比较的值left和right,即收缩为了两个值        if (nums[left] == target) return left; // 比较left是否是目标值        if (nums[right] == target) return right; // 比较right是否是目标值        return -1; // 没有找到    &#125;&#125;</code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
    
